# LAst amended: 3rd JAn, 2025

# 1.0 First install uv
# Ref: https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-started/installation/#installation-methods
$ curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh

# 1.1 Close and open Ubuntu WSL again

# 1.2 Install langflow
# Ref: https://docs.langflow.org/get-started-installation
$ uv pip install langflow

# 1.3 Run langflow:
$ uv run langflow run

# 1.4 Acccess it, at:
http://127.0.0.1:7860 

# 1.5 It is possible that Symantic antivirus
#     will not allow langflow start. Then
#     Press win+R and run the following command:

    smc -stop

############# DONE #############
